N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4220.8 - Registration of stable name

State Regulations

An individual or partnership may adopt a stable name
under which to race horses which does not conflict with another stable name. All stable names shall be filed with and be subject to the approval or
disapproval of the commission. Notes
